                     <interp inst="t18700404-360-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, Stealing one bag, and 12<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in money, of <persName id="t18700404-name-324" type="victimName">
